      <title>法官责骂司法律师因未能遵守驱逐命令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/judge-scolds-doj-lawyer-over-failure-to-obey-deportation-order</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名联邦法官告诫司法部的律师，因为上周末未能服从他的口头命令，以使美国政府停止驱逐出境，涉嫌委内瑞拉帮派成员最终被萨尔瓦多的一名监狱驱逐出境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/judge-scolds-doj-lawyer-over-failure-to-obey-deportation-order</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Mar 2025 20:50:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
