      <title>目前，法院规定将25,000名被解雇的联邦工人从事工作</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/court-rules-to-keep-25-000-fired-federal-workers-in-jobs-for-now</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联邦上诉法院裁定，特朗普政府必须继续遵守马里兰州法官的命令，以临时恢复25,000名美国机构的雇员至少一周。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/court-rules-to-keep-25-000-fired-federal-workers-in-jobs-for-now</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Mar 2025 20:46:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
